{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kaskade is a minimalist strategy game about connecting an evolving delivery network. It's about getting into a state of flow and painting a picture with a minimal toolset.\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/Build.gif?t=1737549603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Connect inputs to outputs that match in color to earn credits. Spend credits to unlock new abilities. Use those new abilities to make managing your network more effective. Rinse and repeat.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/Combine.gif?t=1737549603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Permadeath!\u00a0Too many false moves and it will be game over! There is no save system, but there is roguelite progression between runs.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/ItemPickup.gif?t=1737549603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A zen, puzzle experience or a strategic, roguelite challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5 Chapters with unique mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Three game modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Normal for the classic Kaskade experience,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Infinite for stress-free sandbox play,</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hard for a serious challenge</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Key abilities to unlock (Jump, Double Jump, Switch, Compact, and Pause)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Boons and upgrades to purchase to manage more and more deliveries</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Colorblind mode (deliveries have clear labels)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mouse and keyboard support (gamepads are not recommended)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737549603","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/page.bg.jpg?t=1737549603","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/6c105b90db42833fcb5fe2a404dc90c2672485ac/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737549603","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/6c105b90db42833fcb5fe2a404dc90c2672485ac/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737549603","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kaskade is a minimalist strategy game about connecting an evolving delivery network. It's about getting into a state of flow and painting a picture with a minimal toolset.\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/Build.gif?t=1737549603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Connect inputs to outputs that match in color to earn credits. Spend credits to unlock new abilities. Use those new abilities to make managing your network more effective. Rinse and repeat.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285530/extras/Combine.gif?t=1737549603\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Permadeath!\u00a0Too many false moves and it will be game over! There is no save system,